3846, "You failed to protect the Hope.  Even though we were not expecting an attack from the Shivans, you needed to protect that ship.  Due to your failure, our hold on this sector becomes even more tenuous.  We all have to perform beyond our abilities in this war, Pilot.  Dismissed!"

