3847, "$h Red $h Alert!  The Beta Aquilae installation is under attack.  The Lucifer has been sighted in the area.  Protect it at all costs.  Additional orders will be given to you on site."

3848, "Protecting all the escape pods is most impressive.  The survivors thank you and hope we can avenge the destruction of the Aquilae."

3849, "By protecting the Beta Aquilae Communications Terminal we are able to keep in contact with our forces in the outer systems.  Losing the communication terminal would have been a severe blow.  Well done pilot.

For continued service to the Alliance, we are awarding you the Good Conduct Medal.  Keep it up."

3850, "We lost many escape pods in the battle as well.  Such a loss of life is difficult to bear.  Several key scientists were unable to evacuate the installation.  They, and their research, will be sorely missed."

3851, "Disobeying orders and departing during battle is inexcusable.  You are indefinitely grounded.  Dismissed."

